<L><PB N="80" REF="79">
<MILESTONE N="245">'Tis ours this &s;on of &s;orrow to relieve,</L>
<L>Chear the &s;ad heart, nor let affliction grieve.</L>
<L>By <HI>Jove</HI> the &s;tranger and the poor are &s;ent,</L>
