<L>Heav'n on that hour its choice&s;t influence &s;hed,</L>
<L>That gave a &s;ov'reign &s;pou&s;e to crown her bed!</L>
<L>All, all the god-like worthies that adorn</L>
<L><MILESTONE N="340">This realm, &s;he flies: <HI>Phaeacia</HI> is her &s;corn.&endq;</L>
<L>And ju&s;t the blame: for female innocence</L>
<L>Not only flies the guilt, but &s;huns th' offence:</L>
