<L><PB N="180" REF="174">
They launch the ve&s;&s;el, and unfurl the &s;ails,</L>
<L>And &s;tretch the &s;welling canvas to the gales;</L>
<L>Then to the palace move: A gath'ring throng,</L>
<L><MILESTONE N="50">Youth, and white age, tumultuous pour along:</L>
